/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2857533489/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2857533489/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2857533489/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2857533489","tinyui":"/x/MYBSqg","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2857533489","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2857533489/Tasking+y+Estimaci+n+-+Red+N1","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2857533489"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"f08c289a-c2ea-48ec-85b9-7591dd17ac61\"><ac:rich-text-body><p>Tasking y estimaci&oacute;n para las tareas del Onboarding de Infonet Cobranzas. Estas tareas est&aacute;n hechas en base al siguiente Figma</p><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/file/RMWUxevSsRLXyu4Q8ibCJO/Infonet-Cobranzas-WEB?type=design&amp;node-id=840-7691&amp;mode=design&amp;t=IZOZAcPY46ag5onc-0\" data-card-appearance=\"block\">https://www.figma.com/file/RMWUxevSsRLXyu4Q8ibCJO/Infonet-Cobranzas-WEB?type=design&amp;node-id=840-7691&amp;mode=design&amp;t=IZOZAcPY46ag5onc-0</a><p> </p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"d116a9ec-5364-4dbf-97e4-4d7ed65f89b9\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 484.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 110.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 166.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Tarea</strong></p></th><th><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Estimaci&oacute;n (hs)</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Comentarios</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>TAREAS FRONTEND</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/file/RMWUxevSsRLXyu4Q8ibCJO/Infonet-Cobranzas-WEB?type=design&amp;node-id=869-837&amp;mode=design&amp;t=IZOZAcPY46ag5onc-0\">Landing Page</a></p><p><em>Vamos a crear esta pantalla siguiendo el mismo esquema de las otras landings, para que sea reutilizable en el caso que quieran cambiar las otras landings a este formato</em></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">40</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/file/RMWUxevSsRLXyu4Q8ibCJO/Infonet-Cobranzas-WEB?type=design&amp;node-id=903-553&amp;mode=design&amp;t=IZOZAcPY46ag5onc-4\">Seleccionar Dispositivo</a></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">24</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/file/RMWUxevSsRLXyu4Q8ibCJO/Infonet-Cobranzas-WEB?type=design&amp;node-id=869-837&amp;mode=design&amp;t=IZOZAcPY46ag5onc-4\">Seleccionar Tipo de Operaci&oacute;n Bancaria para Capital Propio</a></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">28</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffebe6\"><p><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/proto/RMWUxevSsRLXyu4Q8ibCJO/Infonet-Cobranzas-WEB?type=design&amp;node-id=869-837&amp;t=IZOZAcPY46ag5onc-0&amp;scaling=min-zoom&amp;page-id=840%3A7691\">Seleccionar Tipo de Operaci&oacute;n Bancaria para Cuenta TIC</a></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffebe6\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffebe6\"><p>No est&aacute; contemplada para esta etapa</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffebe6\"><p><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/proto/RMWUxevSsRLXyu4Q8ibCJO/Infonet-Cobranzas-WEB?type=design&amp;node-id=871-1762&amp;t=IZOZAcPY46ag5onc-0&amp;scaling=min-zoom&amp;page-id=840%3A7691\">Pantalla para Adjuntar Documentos</a></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffebe6\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffebe6\"><p>No est&aacute; contemplada para esta etapa</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffebe6\"><p><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/file/RMWUxevSsRLXyu4Q8ibCJO/Infonet-Cobranzas-WEB?type=design&amp;node-id=858-11126&amp;mode=design&amp;t=IZOZAcPY46ag5onc-4\">Pantalla de Incluir POS</a></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffebe6\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\" /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffebe6\"><p>No est&aacute; contemplada para esta etapa</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/file/RMWUxevSsRLXyu4Q8ibCJO/Infonet-Cobranzas-WEB?type=design&amp;node-id=903-827&amp;mode=design&amp;t=IZOZAcPY46ag5onc-4\">Loader Procesando</a></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/file/RMWUxevSsRLXyu4Q8ibCJO/Infonet-Cobranzas-WEB?type=design&amp;node-id=903-832&amp;mode=design&amp;t=IZOZAcPY46ag5onc-4\">Modal de Solicitud Exitosa</a></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>Modal de Solicitud Rechazada</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>Falta dise&ntilde;o</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>TAREAS BACKEND</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>Crear endpoint en commerce-service para consultar las cuentas</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>24</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>Crear operaci&oacute;n en external-services para consultar a redise&ntilde;o</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>20</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p /></td></tr></tbody></table><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"panel\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"97f96463-4be9-4513-9cec-f012b954b5bc\"><ac:parameter ac:name=\"panelIcon\">:note:</ac:parameter><ac:parameter ac:name=\"panelIconId\">atlassian-note</ac:parameter><ac:parameter ac:name=\"bgColor\">#EAE6FF</ac:parameter><ac:rich-text-body><p>Preguntas</p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"6996b6a1-05ed-489a-ba8f-81535c93c339\"><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Pregunta</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Respuesta</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>Esto es para usuarios deslogueados que quieren contratar un servicio, o para usuarios ya existentes? Nos genera la duda, porque en el caso que sean usuarios existentes porque se pide igualmente documentaci&oacute;n al final?</p></td><td><p>Para comercios existentes en base a este doc: </p><p><a href=\"https://bancard.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/PMIC/pages/206405892/Onboarding+-+Portal+de+Comercios\" data-card-appearance=\"inline\">https://bancard.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/PMIC/pages/206405892/Onboarding+-+Portal+de+Comercios</a> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>En la pantalla para seleccionar como el usuario quiere operar con el servicio, tenemos la opci&oacute;n para seleccionar una cuenta TIC.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/file/RMWUxevSsRLXyu4Q8ibCJO/Infonet-Cobranzas-WEB?type=design&amp;node-id=869-837&amp;mode=design&amp;t=IZOZAcPY46ag5onc-4\">Figma</a></p><p>Esto es para abrir una cuenta de sobregiro? </p></td><td><p>Si. </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>En la pantalla para seleccionar como el usuario quiero operar con el servicio, en la opci&oacute;n de &ldquo;Capital Propio&rdquo;, tenemos T&eacute;rminos y Condiciones. </p><p>Como se pretende que sea este formato? Si una web, un pdf? </p><p><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/proto/RMWUxevSsRLXyu4Q8ibCJO/Infonet-Cobranzas-WEB?type=design&amp;node-id=869-1080&amp;t=IZOZAcPY46ag5onc-0&amp;scaling=min-zoom&amp;page-id=840%3A7691\">Figma</a></p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>En la pantalla para seleccionar como quiere operar el usuario, de donde vamos a traer la informaci&oacute;n de todos los Bancos? <br /><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/file/RMWUxevSsRLXyu4Q8ibCJO/Infonet-Cobranzas-WEB?type=design&amp;node-id=869-837&amp;mode=design&amp;t=IZOZAcPY46ag5onc-4\">Figma</a></p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>En la pantalla para seleccionar como quiere operar el usuario, como quieren que funcione el buscador? </p><p><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/file/RMWUxevSsRLXyu4Q8ibCJO/Infonet-Cobranzas-WEB?type=design&amp;node-id=869-837&amp;mode=design&amp;t=IZOZAcPY46ag5onc-4\">Figma</a></p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>En que etapa del flujo va la pantalla de incluir POS?<br /><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/file/RMWUxevSsRLXyu4Q8ibCJO/Infonet-Cobranzas-WEB?type=design&amp;node-id=858-11126&amp;mode=design&amp;t=IZOZAcPY46ag5onc-4\">Figma</a></p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>Al finalizar una solicitud, tenemos dise&ntilde;o para solicitud exitosa, pero no para cuando falla</p><p><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/file/RMWUxevSsRLXyu4Q8ibCJO/Infonet-Cobranzas-WEB?type=design&amp;node-id=903-832&amp;mode=design&amp;t=IZOZAcPY46ag5onc-4\">Figma</a></p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>Para crear la oportunidad comercial, nos sirve la operaci&oacute;n <code>create_commercial_opportunity_with_item</code> ?</p><p>Qu&eacute; par&aacute;metros mandamos en <code>opportunity_name, product_id, device_id, cost_id, quantity ?</code></p></td><td><p /></td></tr></tbody></table><p />","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/3048144919"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":2963},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3048144919/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3048144919/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3048144919/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3048144919/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3048144919","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3048144919/Onboarding+Infonet+Cobranzas+-+Tasking+y+Estimaci+n","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3048144919","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3048144919","tinyui":"/x/FwCvtQ","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}